The following are commands to run the sample program under the src directory.
It demonstrates how to use the Cascading extensions for Accumulo to perform table operations.


a) Run the program with parameter createTable
====================================================

hadoop jar cascadingSamples/accumuloTapSample/jars/tableOperationsSample.jar TableOperationsSample "accumulo://sherlock?instance=indra&user=root&password=xxxxxxx&zookeepers=cdh-dn01:2181" "createTable"

Verify in Accumulo
===================
root@indra GENetwork> tables
!METADATA
GENetwork
sherlock
trace

b) Run the program with parameter createTableWithSplits
========================================================

hadoop jar cascadingSamples/accumuloTapSample/jars/tableOperationsSample.jar TableOperationsSample "accumulo://watson?instance=indra&user=root&password= xxxxxxx&zookeepers=cdh-dn01:2181" "createTableWithSplits" "D,L"
 
Verify in Accumulo
===================
root@indra GENetwork> tables
!METADATA
GENetwork
sherlock
trace
watson

c) Run the program with parameter checkIfTableExists
====================================================

hadoop jar cascadingSamples/accumuloTapSample/jars/tableOperationsSample.jar TableOperationsSample "accumulo://watson?instance=indra&user=root&password= xxxxxxx&zookeepers=cdh-dn01:2181" "checkIfTableExists"
....
The table exists!

hadoop jar cascadingSamples/accumuloTapSample/jars/tableOperationsSample.jar TableOperationsSample "accumulo://maachuPichu?instance=indra&user=root&password= xxxxxxx&zookeepers=cdh-dn01:2181" "checkIfTableExists"
...
The table  does not exist!

d) Run the program with parameter deleteTable
====================================================

hadoop jar cascadingSamples/accumuloTapSample/jars/tableOperationsSample.jar TableOperationsSample "accumulo://sherlock?instance=indra&user=root&password= xxxxxxx&zookeepers=cdh-dn01:2181" "deleteTable" 
..
The table was deleted successfully!

Verify in Accumulo
==================

root@indra GENetwork> tables
!METADATA
GENetwork
trace
watson


